WEBVTT

00:00:00.468 --> 00:00:02.452
Track 05.03

00:00:04.048 --> 00:00:05.476
Narrator: 1

00:00:06.349 --> 00:00:09.048
A: Is there a bath in the room?

00:00:09.325 --> 00:00:13.929
B: No, there isn’t. But there is a shower.

00:00:15.198 --> 00:00:16.468
Narrator: 2

00:00:17.579 --> 00:00:21.230
A: There aren’t any hotels in this town.

00:00:21.587 --> 00:00:22.738
B: Oh!

00:00:23.175 --> 00:00:26.547
A: There’s a hostel on King Street.

00:00:26.746 --> 00:00:28.135
It’s very good.

00:00:28.611 --> 00:00:31.111
B: OK. Thanks.

00:00:32.302 --> 00:00:33.651
Narrator: 3

00:00:34.619 --> 00:00:37.952
B: Is there a car park for this hotel?

00:00:38.389 --> 00:00:40.651
A: Yes, there is.

00:00:41.213 --> 00:00:42.421
B: Are there any empty

00:00:42.453 --> 00:00:44.582
rooms on the ground floor?

00:00:44.979 --> 00:00:48.629
A: No, there aren’t. Sorry.

00:00:49.186 --> 00:00:50.477
There are a lot

00:00:50.502 --> 00:00:52.994
of empty rooms on the top floor.

00:00:53.591 --> 00:00:56.750
B: Oh … No thanks.